JW2   * IF DUPLICATE, DISPLAY ORDER# FIELD BY REVERSE MODE
 .    * COUNTER FOR BLANK (ID)
 .   C                     Z-ADD0         B@CNT   40
 .    * COUNTER FOR OTHER THAN D/BLANK (ID)
 .   C                     Z-ADD0         N@CNT   40
 .   C                     MOVELACEDID    YCEDID
 .   C                     MOVELACPLNT    YCPLNT
 .   C                     MOVELACSHCD    YCSHCD
 .   C                     MOVELACODRN    YCODRN
 .   C                     MOVELACPLSH    YCPLSH
